body.description: Get the superior performance and softness you’ve been waiting for with Cottonelle FreshFeel Flushable Wet Wipes, designed to leave you comfortably dry. Each pack has 42 flushable wet wipes per pack so you can worry less about running out when you or guests at your home need it most. Looking for more ways to feel clean down there after taking care of business? Use Cottonelle toilet paper to feel shower fresh. Conveniently remain stocked on flushable wipes by ordering Cottonelle for delivery to your door or pickup curbside. Cottonelle cares about you and our planet. We are proud to be FSC certified ensuring the forests we source from are responsibly managed to prevent deforestation and help protect the trees and animals that depend on them. We also use fibers that are 100% plant-based with no harsh chemicals or dyes.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars They offer a perfect blend of quality, quantity
reviews.reviewText: Having tried numerous brands in search of the perfect flushable wet wipes, the Cottonelle FreshFeel Flushable Wet Wipes have emerged as an absolute game-changer in personal hygiene.These wipes come in a convenient pack of 8 flip-top packs, each containing 42 wipes, offering a total of 336 wipes. The packaging may vary, but the quality remains consistently exceptional.What truly sets Cottonelle apart is its unparalleled balance between effectiveness and gentleness. The wipes are adequately moist without being overly wet, ensuring a thorough cleansing experience while being gentle on the skin.Having explored various options, Cottonelle's wipes stand out for their durability and reliability. They don't tear easily and retain their moisture, even after repeated use, ensuring a consistent and refreshing experience every time.Moreover, the flushability of these wipes is remarkable, giving peace of mind with their ability to break down and disperse after flushing. This eco-friendly feature aligns perfectly with the convenience of using wet wipes without the guilt of environmental impact.In comparison to other brands, Cottonelle FreshFeel Flushable Wet Wipes undoubtedly outshine the competition. They offer a perfect blend of quality, quantity, and reliability, making them a staple in maintaining personal hygiene. The smells is yummy the thickness is perfect.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Experience the Ultimate Cleanliness and Comfort with Cottonelle FreshFeel Flushable Wet Wipes!
reviews.reviewText: In the quest for the cleanest and most comfortable bathroom experience, Cottonelle FreshFeel Flushable Wet Wipes stand head and shoulders above the rest. This 8-pack of flushable wipes is more than just a bathroom essential; it's a game-changer in personal hygiene.Let's dive into the details. This package includes 8 convenient flip-top packs, each containing 42 flushable wipes. That's a total of 336 flushable wipes at your disposal. No more running out of wipes when you need them the most – Cottonelle has you covered.The true magic of these wipes lies in their ability to provide a healthy and gentle clean. They offer premium softness that's not only comfortable but also safe for sensitive skin. Whether you're using them for yourself or your family, you'll appreciate the level of comfort they bring to your daily routine.But what sets Cottonelle apart is its commitment to safety and cleanliness. These flushable wipes are septic-safe, ensuring that they won't harm your plumbing or the environment. They not only clean your hands and bottom effectively but also provide a peace of mind that you're making an eco-conscious choice.For the ultimate clean, consider combining Cottonelle flushable wet wipes with Cottonelle toilet paper. Together, they deliver a refreshing and shower-fresh clean that leaves you feeling revitalized and ready to tackle your day with confidence.Cottonelle takes sustainability seriously. Their products are FSC certified, which means they source their materials from responsibly managed forests to prevent deforestation. Plus, their wipes are made from 100% plant-based fibers and are free of harsh chemicals. You can feel good about using a product that cares for your well-being and the environment.In summary, Cottonelle FreshFeel Flushable Wet Wipes are not just wipes; they are an investment in cleanliness, comfort, and sustainability. With their ample supply, gentle cleaning, and commitment to eco-friendliness, they are a must-have in every bathroom. Elevate your personal hygiene game with Cottonelle and experience the difference for yourself!
